        <item>
            <title>《刺客教条：暗影者》开放预购，登上 PS5、PC、Xbox X/S 等平台</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/01/24/assassins-creed-shadows-3/game-channel/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=assassins-creed-shadows-3</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2025/01/24/assassins-creed-shadows-3/game-channel/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Lawton]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Fri, 24 Jan 2025 06:30:54 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[游戏情报]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Assassin's Creed Shadows]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1288597</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>Ubisoft 宣布《刺客教条》系列全新作品《刺客教条：暗影者》现已开放预购，并将于 3 月 20 日全球同步推出。预购玩家将可免费获得「淡路猎爪」扩充内容，该内容包含新地区、新技能以及超过 10 小时的额外游戏时间。游戏将登陆 PlayStation 5、Xbox Series X|S、配备 Apple 晶片的 Mac（Mac App Store）、Windows PC（包括 Ubisoft Store、Steam、Epic Games Store）和 Amazon Luna 平台。</p><p><img fetchpriority="high" decoding="async" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1288617 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/acsh_embargo_keyart_-580x580.jpg" alt="" width="580" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/acsh_embargo_keyart_-580x580.jpg 580w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/acsh_embargo_keyart_.jpg 900w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/acsh_embargo_keyart_-144x144.jpg 144w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 580px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1288601" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/acsh_147_screenshot_-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/acsh_147_screenshot_-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/acsh_147_screenshot_.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1288602 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/acsh_149_screenshot_-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/acsh_149_screenshot_-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/acsh_149_screenshot_.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><h2>穿越至 16 世纪日本的史诗冒险</h2><p>由 Ubisoft 魁北克工作室主导开发的《刺客教条：暗影者》，将玩家带入 16 世纪的日本，探索忍术专家伊贺女刺客奈绪江和传奇武士弥助之间错综复杂的故事。在这片动荡的土地上，两位主角将在日本统一的历史进程中与大名织田信长的野心正面交锋。游戏的剧情预告片揭示了两人如何在内忧外患的背景下，共同开创新教条的未来。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1288600" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/acsh_113_screenshot_-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/acsh_113_screenshot_-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/acsh_113_screenshot_.jpg 1024w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1288604" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/acsh_164_screenshot_-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/acsh_164_screenshot_-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/acsh_164_screenshot_.jpg 1024w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1288605" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/acsh_165_screenshot_-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/acsh_165_screenshot_-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/acsh_165_screenshot_.jpg 1024w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1288606" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/acsh_166_screenshot_-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/acsh_166_screenshot_-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/acsh_166_screenshot_.jpg 1024w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><h2>多版本选择与专属内容</h2><p>《刺客教条：暗影者》将推出标准版、数码豪华版及典藏版，满足不同玩家需求：</p><ul><li><strong>数码豪华版</strong>：包含游戏主程式、「赤龙双组合包」（包括奈绪江和弥助的专属装备与武器）、「赤龙藏身处组合包」（提供藏身处外观）以及「精通点数」。</li><li><strong>典藏版</strong>：除豪华版数码内容外，还包括实体收藏品，如 Steelbook 铁盒、世界地图、奈绪江与弥助公仔、武士刀刀镡、壁挂教条卷轴、76 页艺术图集及两幅水墨画印刷作品。</li></ul><h2>预购福利：免费扩充内容与专属任务</h2><p>预购任何版本的玩家将可免费获得将于 2025 年稍后推出的「淡路猎爪」扩充内容。这项 DLC 增加全新开放区域，带来更多游戏时间、新技能和装备。奈绪江更将获得新武器「棒」（Bō），协助对抗淡路岛上的危险势力「山贼派」。此外，预购玩家还可解锁专属任务「狗命坎坷」，该任务将于游戏发售时提供。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1288607" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/acsh_172_screenshot_-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/acsh_172_screenshot_-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/acsh_172_screenshot_.jpg 1024w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1288608" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/acsh_181_screenshot_-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/acsh_181_screenshot_-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/acsh_181_screenshot_.jpg 1024w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1288609" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/acsh_coa_naoe_kick_t-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/acsh_coa_naoe_kick_t-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/acsh_coa_naoe_kick_t.jpg 1024w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1288610" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/acsh_coa_naoe_kick_t-1-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/acsh_coa_naoe_kick_t-1-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/acsh_coa_naoe_kick_t-1.jpg 1024w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1288611" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/acsh_coa_vista-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/acsh_coa_vista-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/acsh_coa_vista.jpg 1024w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2025/01/24/assassins-creed-shadows-3/game-channel/">《刺客教条：暗影者》开放预购，登上 PS5、PC、Xbox X/S 等平台</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
