        <item>
            <title>FUJIFILM 最抢手即影即有出 Wide 版    「instax WIDE Evo」大玩不同摄影效果 + 影到靓先印</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/01/23/instax-wide-evo/dc/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=instax-wide-evo</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2025/01/23/instax-wide-evo/dc/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Lawton]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Thu, 23 Jan 2025 12:00:44 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[数码相机]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[instax WIDE Evo]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1288483</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>Fujifilm 宣布推出全新混合式即影即有相机「instax WIDE Evo」，Evo 上代一出即卖断市，今代 WIDE Evo 就支援宽幅 WIDE 格式菲林，厂方称可实现多达 10 万种摄影效果选择。相机预计于 2025 年 2 月 6 日发售，售价为 HKD 2,798。</p><h4></h4><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1288486" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/whatsappimage2025012-580x580.jpeg" alt="" width="580" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/whatsappimage2025012-580x580.jpeg 580w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/whatsappimage2025012.jpeg 900w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/whatsappimage2025012-144x144.jpeg 144w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 580px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1288487" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/whatsappimage2025012-1-694x462.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/whatsappimage2025012-1-694x462.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/whatsappimage2025012-1.jpeg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1288495" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/highresinstaxwideevo-3-580x580.jpg" alt="" width="580" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/highresinstaxwideevo-3-580x580.jpg 580w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/highresinstaxwideevo-3.jpg 900w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/highresinstaxwideevo-3-144x144.jpg 144w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 580px" /></p><p>「instax WIDE Evo」延续传统菲林相机的操作理念，机身采用黑色基调搭配金属质感，复古外观更添奢华感。相机配备 LCD 屏幕，支援用户即时取景，并挑选心仪照片打印。相机更加入「玩味」设计，用户可手动操作菲林转盘及列印摇杆，可以手动把印好的菲林「搅」出来，模拟传统相机体验，进一步提升即影即有相机的趣味性。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1288494" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/highresinstaxwideevo-2-580x580.jpg" alt="" width="580" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/highresinstaxwideevo-2-580x580.jpg 580w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/highresinstaxwideevo-2.jpg 900w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/highresinstaxwideevo-2-144x144.jpg 144w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 580px" /></p><h4></h4><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1288492" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/highresinstaxwideevo-580x580.jpg" alt="" width="580" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/highresinstaxwideevo-580x580.jpg 580w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/highresinstaxwideevo.jpg 900w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/highresinstaxwideevo-144x144.jpg 144w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 580px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1288488" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/whatsappimage2025012-2-580x580.jpeg" alt="" width="580" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/whatsappimage2025012-2-580x580.jpeg 580w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/whatsappimage2025012-2.jpeg 900w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/whatsappimage2025012-2-144x144.jpeg 144w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 580px" /></p><p>新一代「WIDE Evo」提供 10 种菲林效果（如「品红」和「黑白」）及 10 种镜头效果（如「漏光」和「色彩渐变」），并加入首次推出的「微调」功能，用户可细致调整光线强度和色彩渐变，达到 100 级的精确调节。这种效果的组合与微调，令摄影选项多达 100,000 种，让每张作品更具创意。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1288484 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2025012342716-571x580.jpg" alt="" width="571" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2025012342716-571x580.jpg 571w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2025012342716.jpg 886w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 571px" /></p><p>WIDE Evo 新增「菲林风格」与「广角模式」两大功能。「菲林风格」提供六种风格化相框设计，使照片更具艺术感；而「广角模式」则进一步扩展画面范围，适合拍摄壮丽风景或热闹场景。</p><div class="mceTemp"></div><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1288485 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2025012342706-551x580.jpg" alt="" width="551" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2025012342706-551x580.jpg 551w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2025012342706.jpg 856w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 551px" /></p><p>专属手机应用程式提供「探索动态」功能，让用户浏览全球「WIDE Evo」作品，从中获取灵感。应用程式亦支援效果复制，用户可透过蓝牙将其他作品的效果复制至自己的相机，轻松实现个性化创作。除此之外，相机还可作为智能手机打印机，直接列印手机内的照片。配合「instax WIDE Evo」的推出，富士还同步推出专用相机保护套（HKD 400）及全新 WIDE 格式菲林「磨砂金属感」（HKD 120），以丰富用户的摄影选择。</p><div class="page" title="Page 7"><div class="section"><img decoding="async" src="data:image/png;base64," alt="page7image57853248" width="98.784000" height="0.960000" /><img decoding="async" src="data:image/png;base64," alt="page7image57865728" width="218.300000" height="0.959990" /><img decoding="async" src="data:image/png;base64," alt="page7image57866688" width="133.700000" height="0.959990" /><img decoding="async" src="data:image/png;base64," alt="page7image57867072" width="98.784000" height="0.959990" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1288493" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/highresinstaxwideevo-1-580x580.jpg" alt="" width="580" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/highresinstaxwideevo-1-580x580.jpg 580w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/highresinstaxwideevo-1.jpg 900w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/highresinstaxwideevo-1-144x144.jpg 144w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 580px" /><img decoding="async" src="data:image/png;base64," alt="page7image57866880" width="218.300000" height="0.480010" /><img decoding="async" src="data:image/png;base64," alt="page7image57862848" width="133.700000" height="0.480010" /><img decoding="async" src="data:image/png;base64," alt="page7image57867264" width="98.784000" height="0.480010" /><img decoding="async" src="data:image/png;base64," alt="page7image57867456" width="218.300000" height="0.480000" /><img decoding="async" src="data:image/png;base64," alt="page7image57867648" width="133.700000" height="0.480000" /><img decoding="async" src="data:image/png;base64," alt="page7image57867840" width="98.784000" height="0.480000" /><img decoding="async" src="data:image/png;base64," alt="page7image57868032" width="218.300000" height="0.960010" /><img decoding="async" src="data:image/png;base64," alt="page7image57802944" width="133.700000" height="0.960010" /><img decoding="async" src="data:image/png;base64," alt="page7image57805056" width="98.784000" height="0.960010" /></div></div><p>资料来源：Fujifilm</p><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2025/01/23/instax-wide-evo/dc/">FUJIFILM 最抢手即影即有出 Wide 版    「instax WIDE Evo」大玩不同摄影效果 + 影到靓先印</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
